node.text: Though her career began in classical music, painting, and analog photography, @HelenaGarza_'s field of inspiration is boundless. In this project, she shares a VR painting – a proposal of reality understood from figurative memories and the present environment in constant change and reconstruction. Learn more about her unique explorations in art at vans.com/offthewall
